{"3913950": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "LA: Streets of Sorcery", "steam_appid": 3913950, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>Two New Demos Await You</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3913950/extras/ae74009a8a573243a71cb1b94a3b3596.poster.avif?t=1774957977\" width=780 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3913950/extras/ae74009a8a573243a71cb1b94a3b3596.webm?t=1774957977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3913950/extras/ae74009a8a573243a71cb1b94a3b3596.mp4?t=1774957977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>關於此遊戲</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>慾望學院：魔法街道</strong> 是一部魔法、幽默與性愛碰撞的偵探視覺小說。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您將扮演一位加入魔法部非法魔法司的年輕人。您的新搭檔——一位言辭犀利的褐髮女郎——可能比您追捕的罪犯帶來更多混亂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3913950/extras/fca915685f825794fadafa5b6030c5e3.poster.avif?t=1774957977\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3913950/extras/fca915685f825794fadafa5b6030c5e3.webm?t=1774957977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3913950/extras/fca915685f825794fadafa5b6030c5e3.mp4?t=1774957977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個章節都呈現一個全新的案件，融合了<strong>神秘、幽默和成人場景</strong>。您的選擇將塑造調查過程、浪漫關係，甚至最終結局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>獨特的世界觀</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >都市奇幻設定，魔法與法師就生活在我們中間，只是小心翼翼地隱藏在公眾視野之外</p></